01:04:57.500 --> 01:04:59.940
Dia mungkin pergi jumpa kawan peguam dia, Cik Cha.

01:04:59.940 --> 01:05:01.270
Pergi cari di Penerbangan Malam juga.

01:05:01.270 --> 01:05:03.710
Kalau dia tak ada di sana, tunggu di rumah.

01:05:05.270 --> 01:05:06.880
Saya nak tolong awak cari...

01:05:07.540 --> 01:05:09.110
